03:33.923 --> 03:34.923
Saroo, catch!

03:40.721 --> 03:44.016
Hey! Hey!

03:45.267 --> 03:46.267
Get down!

03:48.354 --> 03:49.563
Guddu! The guards!

03:50.105 --> 03:51.232
Hey!

03:52.066 --> 03:53.317
Hey, boy, get down!

03:56.695 --> 03:57.947
Go! Get down, boy!

04:10.334 --> 04:13.712
