- Guddu!

04:28.978 --> 04:29.978
Saroo.

04:31.272 --> 04:32.272
I'm here.

04:32.314 --> 04:34.400
We will get a lot of money today.

04:34.650 --> 04:36.277
We've got a lot of coal!

04:36.527 --> 04:37.820
Show me!

04:38.362 --> 04:39.613
Ohhh, so much!

04:40.948 --> 04:43.534
You kept telling me how little I am...

04:43.784 --> 04:45.160
...but see how clever I am?

04:45.661 --> 04:47.871
That's right, you are!

04:48.122 --> 04:50.124
You jumped from so high! What a leap!

04:50.374 --> 04:51.917
Yes great heights!

04:59.258 --> 05:00.926
Give them some milk - two packets.

05:09.184 --> 05:10.686
Guddu, I want some jalebis!

05:14.315 --> 05:16.608
One day I will buy you some jalebis.

05:16.859 --> 05:18.652
We'll buy the whole shop.

05:19.486 --> 05:20.486
Ha, alright.

05:28.787 --> 05:29.827
Which way should I go now?

05:29.913 --> 05:30.913
Left, left!

05:31.457 --> 05:32.583
Which way now?

05:33.000 --> 05:34.000
Right, right.

05:39.798 --> 05:41.342
Do you want to drink some milk?

05:48.932 --> 05:50.100
I got some milk!

05:51.143 --> 05:52.394
Hey.

06:00.527 --> 06:01.862
It's magic.

06:06.784 --> 06:07.785
Tell me now...

06:08.494 --> 06:10.287
...how did you get the milk?

06:11.455 --> 06:12.455
Be honest.

06:15.417 --> 06:17.586
Guddu? Saroo?

06:30.724 --> 06:31.724
No.

06:38.732 --> 06:40.567
Okay, Shekila, I have to work now.

06:42.486 --> 06:44.363
Who's going to look after Shekila?

06:46.198 --> 06:47.198
My Saroo?

06:51.370 --> 06:52.621
Come. Eat.

06:53.622 --> 06:56.625
Sleep... Sleep.

07:06.009 --> 07:07.261
How long will you be away for?

07:07.511 --> 07:08.929
You did a really good job today.

07:16.937 --> 07:18.105
I want to come too.

07:20.399 --> 07:21.650
How many days?

07:22.067 --> 07:23.402
I'm going for a week.

07:23.694 --> 07:25.404
Who's going to look after Shekila?

07:25.821 --> 07:26.947
