07:27.364 --> 07:29.241
You're too small to lift bales.

07:29.491 --> 07:30.868
I can lift anything.

07:37.416 --> 07:38.959
Guddu.

07:39.293 --> 07:40.293
Can I come too?

07:40.544 --> 07:42.588
You're too small, you can't do this.

07:42.838 --> 07:44.506
I can lift anything.

07:48.427 --> 07:49.136
Saroo.

07:49.428 --> 07:50.428
I've told you.

07:50.471 --> 07:53.474
It's night work. Not for kids.

07:53.724 --> 07:55.350
Go, go. You're too small.

07:57.478 --> 07:58.562
Saroo, leave it.

07:59.980 --> 08:01.398
I can lift this.

08:08.071 --> 08:09.072
Okay, fine.

08:18.874 --> 08:20.125
Hey, Guddu!

08:20.459 --> 08:22.669
Hey! How are you, Shankar?

09:07.881 --> 09:12.386
Saroo, come on, wake up now!

09:17.599 --> 09:18.599
Saroo, wake up.

09:18.684 --> 09:19.684
I want to sleep.

09:20.310 --> 09:22.104
I want to sleep.

09:22.229 --> 09:23.229
Saroo, wake up

09:23.397 --> 09:25.774
Don't annoy me. I am sleeping.

09:26.066 --> 09:27.066
It's my fault.

09:27.109 --> 09:28.527
I brought you here.

09:28.860 --> 09:30.779
You're too young for the night work.

09:31.071 --> 09:33.448
It's so late.
You will never be able to work.

09:40.330 --> 09:42.249
Saroo,

09:42.457 --> 09:44.257
Saroo, I'm going to find out
about work, okay?

09:44.376 --> 09:46.295
And then I'll come back.

09:46.545 --> 09:48.463
You wait here, don't go anywhere.

09:51.758 --> 09:52.758
Guddu.

09:54.219 --> 09:55.804
Just bring back a hundred jalebis.

09:56.388 --> 09:57.514
You want jalebis?

09:57.764 --> 09:59.349
