10:00.183 --> 10:00.684
Jalebis?

10:01.018 --> 10:02.853
Just wait there. Don't go anywhere.

10:36.887 --> 10:38.472
Guddu?

10:49.900 --> 10:51.485
Guddu?

11:27.062 --> 11:28.647
Guddu?

11:32.401 --> 11:33.985
Guddu?

12:33.754 --> 12:34.921
Help me!

12:39.885 --> 12:40.885
Guddu!

12:42.304 --> 12:43.889
Guddu!

12:44.139 --> 12:45.139
Help me!

12:45.390 --> 12:46.600
Guddu!

12:46.725 --> 12:47.934
Someone save me!

12:49.811 --> 12:50.811
Guddu!

12:51.938 --> 12:53.940
Help me!

12:55.817 --> 12:56.985
Guddu!

13:39.361 --> 13:42.405
Mum, I love you very much.

13:43.615 --> 13:46.201
