14:11.309 --> 14:12.394
Save me!

14:13.228 --> 14:14.271
Someone help me!

14:15.647 --> 14:17.232
Get me out of here!

14:22.195 --> 14:23.530
Save me...

14:26.950 --> 14:28.285
Get me out of here!

14:28.577 --> 14:29.578
Save me!

14:33.874 --> 14:35.000
Guddu!

14:35.500 --> 14:36.751
Save me!

15:55.956 --> 15:56.956
Open!

16:38.164 --> 16:40.041
Guddu!

16:43.044 --> 16:44.879
Mum!

16:47.590 --> 16:49.300
Guddu!

16:52.387 --> 16:54.097
Mum!

17:03.314 --> 17:04.314
Ganestalay?

17:04.398 --> 17:06.151
Ganestalay?

17:06.526 --> 17:08.611
I want to go home. Ganestalay.

17:12.323 --> 17:13.907
Ganestalay?

17:19.204 --> 17:20.248
Ganestalay?

17:20.415 --> 17:21.415
I don't understand!

17:21.665 --> 17:23.126
I want to go home.

17:23.334 --> 17:24.603
Speak Bengali! I don't understand you.

17:24.627 --> 17:25.627
Move!

17:29.966 --> 17:31.009
Ganestalay?

24:17.290 --> 24:19.876
Don't walk on that, you'll fall off.

24:20.460 --> 24:22.378
What's the matter,
you don't understand Bengali?

24:26.174 --> 24:27.467
Do you understand Hindi?

24:29.218 --> 24:30.344
Yes.

24:31.053 --> 24:32.472
Where are you going?

24:33.681 --> 24:36.267
I have to go home. I am lost.

24:37.477 --> 24:39.037
Did you come from this way or that way?

24:39.854 --> 24:41.189
I don't know which way.

24:41.439 --> 24:42.690
Then how will you go?

24:50.615 --> 24:51.824
What's your name?

24:52.450 --> 24:53.451
Saroo.

24:54.243 --> 24:56.621
My name is Noor.

24:59.874 --> 25:00.958
You're hungry?

25:07.089 --> 25:08.466
Come on...

25:12.053 --> 25:13.471
Come inside.

25:19.143 --> 25:20.143
Come on, come on!

25:32.240 --> 25:35.076
I have to do all this...

25:35.326 --> 25:36.766
...make lunch boxes for all the men.

25:37.453 --> 25:39.330
You have to feed your stomach, you know.

25:41.457 --> 25:43.125
Everybody has to work.

25:43.918 --> 25:46.921
I help my mum...

25:47.213 --> 25:50.633
...to carry rocks.

25:52.093 --> 25:53.094
Your mum carries rocks?

26:04.689 --> 26:05.856
What is this?

26:09.277 --> 26:10.361
Just drink.

26:15.866 --> 26:17.201
Leave some for me!

26:17.451 --> 26:18.911
Huh?

26:45.813 --> 26:48.065
And now a bit of soap...

26:55.823 --> 26:57.700
There is a man...

26:57.992 --> 26:59.869
...and he is called Rama.

27:01.037 --> 27:02.830
He's a very good man.

27:03.080 --> 27:04.915
He helps everyone.

27:06.125 --> 27:08.044
He will help you too.

27:09.920 --> 27:12.423
He's coming tomorrow morning.

27:16.093 --> 27:18.846
Is he going to help me look for my mum?

27:19.180 --> 27:20.306
Mm.

27:21.641 --> 27:27.063
He's going to help you look for your mum.

27:27.605 --> 27:29.065
Hmm?

27:29.440 --> 27:31.484
Close your eyes...

27:32.109 --> 27:33.944
...go to sleep.

27:37.281 --> 27:39.200
Sleep.

27:49.043 --> 27:50.628
Oh, my baby...

27:50.878 --> 27:52.046
...were you sleeping?

27:57.593 --> 28:01.347
I wonder what worlds you've travelled in.

28:01.681 --> 28:03.099
Are you Rama?

28:03.349 --> 28:05.351
Yes, but not the God.

28:17.154 --> 28:18.406
Ah...

28:25.162 --> 28:27.039
Come and lie down.

28:30.334 --> 28:31.334
Come closer.

28:33.087 --> 28:36.173
Do you know, I've come to meet you
from really far away...

28:39.760 --> 28:42.430
...and I want to take you
to a really nice place.

28:43.889 --> 28:45.683
Are you going to take me to Mum?

28:46.100 --> 28:49.478
And from there we're going
to try and look for your mum.

28:50.062 --> 28:52.523
I'll be back tonight...

28:54.442 --> 28:56.152
...and then we'll search.

28:56.444 --> 28:57.695
Huh?

29:10.624 --> 29:11.624
Get up!

29:14.712 --> 29:15.963
Come closer.

29:29.602 --> 29:30.728
Say "thank you".

29:30.936 --> 29:33.439
Thank you.

29:37.902 --> 29:40.112
You've done well.

29:40.654 --> 29:43.657
He's exactly what they're looking for.

29:50.372 --> 29:52.333
