30:04.053 --> 30:05.971
What happened, you didn't drink?

30:07.348 --> 30:08.474
You don't like it?

30:08.891 --> 30:10.267
Hmm?

30:12.311 --> 30:14.605
Why are you down?

30:20.444 --> 30:22.154
Drink this.

30:27.993 --> 30:29.787
♪ Come closer ♪

30:30.996 --> 30:33.123
♪ Come closer ♪

30:33.249 --> 30:34.476
