30:51.058 --> 30:52.685
Saroo!

30:59.024 --> 31:01.026
Saroo!

31:03.737 --> 31:04.780
Saroo!

32:06.634 --> 32:08.177
Good boy!

32:08.677 --> 32:11.138
Good boy!

32:14.099 --> 32:15.392
Go pick up the small ones.

32:16.894 --> 32:19.605
Go pick up the small ones.

32:19.897 --> 32:21.649
Good boy!

32:22.107 --> 32:24.234
Good boy.

32:26.737 --> 32:29.239
Good boy.

32:30.574 --> 32:31.574
Good boy!

32:40.167 --> 32:41.460
Who's my good boy?

32:41.710 --> 32:43.170
Who is it?

32:46.840 --> 32:49.468
I'm sorry, Mum.

34:53.467 --> 34:55.469
So I came out of the cafe...

34:55.719 --> 34:57.096
...and started talking to him.

34:57.513 --> 34:59.313
I realized he doesn't
speak a word of Bengali.

34:59.389 --> 35:01.266
He only speaks Hindi.

35:01.892 --> 35:04.311
I asked him where he was from.

35:04.895 --> 35:07.981
He replied with only one word...
"Ganestalay".

35:08.232 --> 35:09.858
- Ganestalay?
- Ganestalay.

35:10.192 --> 35:11.902
I've never heard of it.

35:13.987 --> 35:15.489
Ganestalay.

35:18.742 --> 35:21.203
Okay, which district is Ganestalay in?

35:21.453 --> 35:23.580
Which district is Ganestalay in?

35:27.000 --> 35:30.295
What is your mother's name?

35:30.838 --> 35:32.131
Mum.

37:10.103 --> 37:11.772
What's your name?

37:12.272 --> 37:13.565
Amita.

37:16.944 --> 37:20.572
This is a very bad place.

37:24.076 --> 37:26.119
Does anybody ever leave here?

37:27.120 --> 37:28.205
I've seen it.

37:29.581 --> 37:31.708
What are you going to do once you leave?

37:32.459 --> 37:34.378
I'm going to buy a watch.

37:50.519 --> 37:51.895
Did you write it?

37:52.646 --> 37:54.356
Hey, Shondeep! What are you doing?

37:55.732 --> 37:56.732
Stop!

37:57.776 --> 37:58.485
Shondeep!

37:58.735 --> 38:00.028
Stop! Stop right now!

38:00.195 --> 38:01.297
Why are you being so naughty?

38:01.321 --> 38:02.321
Shondeep!

38:03.448 --> 38:05.448
Come with me,
I'm going to give you a good beating!

38:08.912 --> 38:10.497
You won't get away with this!

38:27.973 --> 38:30.225
Hey. Hey.

38:31.018 --> 38:32.018
Hey! Shondeep!

38:34.396 --> 38:35.396
Shondeep!

38:35.605 --> 38:36.605
Come on!

38:48.702 --> 38:49.870
Look this way, look this way.

38:50.370 --> 38:51.370
It's me.

38:51.747 --> 38:52.748
It's okay, I'll take him.

38:55.876 --> 38:58.295
Bring him back before morning.

